SemLinker

Packages 
Package Description
configure
This package contains classes used for configuration (api uri, api keys, paths).
evaluation
Classes in this package are related to the evaluation of various aspects of NLP tasks and Semantic annotations.
kbp2013
Package used for the NIST KBP 2013 evaluation campaign experiments.
kbp2013.defineLink
The classes of this package define a link with various methods (query expansion and candidate selection).
kbp2013.externaltools
Classes related to NIST KBP campaign but not directly involved in the process of this prototype.
kbp2013.index
This package contains resources for building Lucene index files used by the application.
kbp2013.managedocuments
This package contains classes to retrieve and normalize KB documents and components before sending them to the API or using them.
kbp2013.managelinkoutput
This package contains classes involved in the generation of final experiment file for KBP evaluation.
kbp2013.tools
Classes devoted to various tasks of the system developed to solve KBP EL task.
kbp2013.wikipedia
Various tools related to usage of Wikipedia XML dumps.
nlp.decoders
Those decoders can be used to extract some specific patterns (related to quantity or energy quantifier) from a sentence.
nlp.upperlevel
The classes in this package are dedicated to improve an annotation using various methods.
semkit.demos
Use these demos to see various applications of the semantic kit.
semkit.extractor
The extractor classes are devoted to retrieving various data.
semkit.semanticresources
This package contains classes related to the use of NLGbAse metadata in a Redis noSQL database.
